===Mosquito bites===
{{main|Insect bites and stings}}

[[Antihistamines]] are effective treatment for the symptoms from bites.<ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.bestbets.org/bets/bet.php?id=1074 |title=BestBets: Oral antihistamines for insect bites |format= |work= |accessdate=}}</ref>  Many diseases such as [[malaria]] are transmitted by [[mosquitoes]].

